      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_02-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "テニスをちゃんと練習したことはないんですけど……",
      "startTime": 8.1042403698,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_02-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "kanaの昔の同級生に、テニス全国クラスの人がいて\nその人のプレイは、たまに観てましたよ",
      "startTime": 17.9709070365,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "press-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_02-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "全国クラスだけあって運動神経も良かったですけど……\nそうそう、球技大会でドッジボールやった時にですね",
      "startTime": 25.5574433804,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_02-kan004.m4a",
      "text": "球がテニスボールより大きいからって、怖がっちゃって\nその場で、一メートル以上ジャンプして避けてました",
      "startTime": 33.7042403698,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-04.m4a",
          "delay": 6329.092963600005,
          "startTime": 36.1666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "press-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_02-kan005.m4a",
      "text": "いや、これ本当なんですよ～！！",
      "startTime": 37.1042403698,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_02-kan006.m4a",
      "text": "いつもはもっと速い球を打ち返してるのに\nビビり過ぎだろって、クラスみんなで大笑いでしたもん",
      "startTime": 42.5375737031,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_laugh-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3362.4262968999974,
          "startTime": 43
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "press-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（kanaさんにそんな同級生がいたとは知らなかったな）\n（いや……今、この場で話を作った可能性もあるか）",
      "startTime": 50.986985488,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（ここはkanaさんのアドリブでなんとかなったけど）\n（コロ子さんはなんでこんなことを……？）",
      "startTime": 58.2294434682,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
