      "text": "一緒に撮った写真上げてるんだけど\nkanaだけ半目で写ってるのを、わざわざ選んでんの",
      "startTime": 79.8204230741,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
