      "text": "（そう言えばkanaさんも前に、似たようなことを）\n（さくらにやってたっけ……いやいや……）",
      "startTime": 86.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "楽屋ではkanaさんを褒めてたのに\nまさか、本番であんな行動に出るとは思いませんでした",
      "startTime": 92.5704307194,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_02-kan010.m4a",
      "text": "しっ、声が大きい\nここ廊下なんだから、誰が聞いてるか分かんないでしょ",
      "startTime": 98.459885963,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_02-kan011.m4a",
      "text": "とにかく。kanaに舐めた真似したからには\nあいつ、タダじゃおかないんだから",
      "startTime": 106.0932192964,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね。俺から抗議を入れておきますので\nkanaさんは明日の撮影もいつも通りに…………あ",
      "startTime": 112.1666661581,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 6745.101960699998,
