      "text": "え？　ごめんなさい、こんなつもりじゃなかった、って\nなんのこと……あ、さっきのインタビューのこと？",
      "startTime": 136.1117640498,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_02-kan015.m4a",
      "text": "さっきkanaと話した時に、自分も似たような感じで\n試合を観たのを思い出して、そっちを話しちゃった？",
      "startTime": 145.0117701533,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_02-kan016.m4a",
      "text": "後からkanaを困らせたことに気付いたけど\nあの場ではリカバリーのしようがなかった……って？",
      "startTime": 152.8117772741,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（あちらから先に言い訳してきたか）\n（それにしても泣き真似してる感じが、なんというか……）",
      "startTime": 160.4333338421,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_02-kan017.m4a",
      "text": "kanaは全然怒ってないから……ほら、泣かないで\nそんなに目をこすったら、メイク落ちちゃうよ",
      "startTime": 169.8812251888,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5124.66567360002,
          "startTime": 175.0058908624
