      "text": "（今回のスポーツメーカーの社長か）\n（こんな所を見られるなんて……あっ、それを狙って？）",
      "startTime": 184.165696323,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_02-kan019.m4a",
      "text": "えっ、kanaがコロ子ちゃんを泣かせてる？\nええと……実はそうなんです",
      "startTime": 192.5698865893,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
